org.glassfish.web.plugin.common

Class WebModuleConfigCommand

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.glassfish.web.plugin.common.WebModuleConfigCommand
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AdminCommand
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ListWebContextParamCommand, ListWebEnvEntryCommand, SetWebContextParamCommand, UnsetWebContextParamCommand, WebEnvEntryCommand

    public abstract class WebModuleConfigCommand
extends Object
implements AdminCommand
    Superclass of all web module config-related commands. All of these commands have the app-name (with perhaps /module-name appended) as a required argument.
    Author:
    tjquinn
